{"id":749,"date":"2023-07-21T12:15:09","date_gmt":"2023-07-21T19:15:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/?page_id=749"},"modified":"2025-07-26T00:09:02","modified_gmt":"2025-07-26T07:09:02","slug":"combination-particles-with-%e3%82%82%e3%81%ae","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/combination-particles-with-%e3%82%82%e3%81%ae\/","title":{"rendered":"Combination Particles with \u3082\u306e"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Combination Particles with \u3082\u306e<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This lesson is about the particle \u3082\u306e and the\u00a0combination particles\u00a0associated with it, not about the nouns \u7269 and \u8005, although all three words share the same origin.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Particle \u3082\u306e: Because<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The particle \u3082\u306e, colloquially as \u3082\u3093, may mean &#8220;because&#8221;. This usage is used extensively by women and\u00a0small children\u00a0as an alternative to \u304b\u3089 and may be used conjunction or as a final particle.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. \u3053\u306e<ruby>\u666f\u8272<rt>\u3051\u3057\u304d<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306f<ruby>\u61d0<rt>\u306a\u3064<\/rt><\/ruby>\u304b\u3057\u3044\u3067\u3059\u306d\u3002\u79c1\u305f\u3061\u304c\u82e5\u3044\u6642\u306b\u51fa\u4f1a\u3063\u305f\u3068\u3053\u308d\u3067\u3059\u3082\u306e\u3002<br>This scenery is nostalgic isn&#8217;t it? It&#8217;s because this is the place we met when we young.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sentence Note<\/strong>: Scenes like above would be commonly heard among old people. &nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. \u306d\u3047\u3001\u306d\u3047\u3001\u3042\u306e\u30d3\u30c7\u30aa\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u8cb7\u3063\u3066\u3088\u3002\u3069\u3046\u3057\u3066\u3082\u3042\u305f\u3057\u307b\u3057\u3044\u3093\u3060\u3082\u306e\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Hey, hey, can you buy that video&nbsp;game? Cause I&#8217;ve got to have it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The particle \u3082\u306e has several other usages.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>&nbsp;1.<\/td><td>&nbsp;Similar to &#8220;will&#8221;, it nominalizes a verb.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>&nbsp;2.<\/td><td>&nbsp;Used with -\u305f\u3044 showing wish, it means &#8220;would like to do&#8221;.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>&nbsp;3.<\/td><td>&nbsp;Ought to.&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>&nbsp;4.<\/td><td>&nbsp;&#8220;\u3088\u304f\u3057\u305f\u3082\u306e\u3060&#8221; means &#8220;used to&#8221;.&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>3. \u3088\u304f\u6cf3\u3044\u3060\u3082\u3093\u3060\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; I used to swim.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>4.&nbsp;<ruby>\u4e38\u6728<rt>\u307e\u308b\u304d<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306f\u6c34\u306b<ruby>\u6d6e<rt>\u3046<\/rt><\/ruby>\u304f\u3082\u306e\u3060\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; A log will float in water.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>5.\u00a0<ruby>\u9be8<rt>\u304f\u3058\u3089<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306b\u306a\u308a\u305f\u3044\u3082\u306e\u3067\u3059\u3002<br>I wish I were a whale.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>6. \u3082\u3063\u3068\u3054\u4e21\u89aa\u306f<ruby>\u656c<rt>\u3046\u3084\u307e<\/rt><\/ruby>\u3046\u3082\u306e\u3067\u3059\u3088\u3002<br>You should be more respectful to your parents.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>7. \u79c1\u3001<ruby>\u6210\u4eba<rt>\u305b\u3044\u3058\u3093<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306b\u306a\u3063\u305f\u3093\u3060\u3082\u306e\u3001\u5c11\u3057\u3050\u3089\u3044\u304a\u9152\u3092\u98f2\u3093\u3067\u3082\u3044\u3044\u3067\u3057\u3087\u3046\u3002<br>I&#8217;m an adult now, so isn&#8217;t it alright for me to have a little liquor to drink?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Combination Particles<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Below is a chart of combination particles with the conjunctive particle \u3082\u306e.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>&nbsp;\uff5e\u3082\u306e\u3067<\/td><td>&nbsp;Shows reason of action for what happened<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>&nbsp;\uff5e\u3082\u306e\u304b<\/td><td>\u00a0Extremely emphatic negation.<br>\uff5e\u306a\u3044\u3082\u306e\u304b shows a feeling of expectation for the realization of an idea and \uff5e\u305f\u3082\u306e\u304b shows a sense of confusion.\u00a0<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>&nbsp;\uff5e\u3082\u306e\u306e<\/td><td>\u00a0&#8220;Even though,&#8221; signifies the unsatisfactory feeling of the speaker.<br>\uff5e\u304b\u3089\u3044\u3044\u3088\u3046\u306a\u3082\u306e\u306e and \uff5e\u3070\u30fb\u3068\u3044\u3044\u3088\u3046\u306a\u3082\u306e\u306e express &#8220;though it&#8217;s OK because&#8221; and &#8220;although it would be for the better if&#8221; respectively.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>&nbsp;\uff5e\u3082\u306e\u3092<\/td><td>&nbsp;Although, if only<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>8. \u3044\u304f\u3064\u304b\u306e<ruby>\u6b20\u70b9<rt>\u3051\u3063\u3066\u3093<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306f\u3042\u308b<strong>\u3082\u306e\u306e<\/strong>\u3001\u5f7c\u306f\u5929\u624d\u3067\u3059\u3002<br>Even though he has a few flaws, he&#8217;s a genius.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>9 \u3042\u3093\u306a\u3084\u3064\u306b\u8ca0\u3051\u308b<strong>\u3082\u3093\u304b<\/strong>\u3044\u3002<br>Like I&#8217;d lose to that kind of guy!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>10. \u8ca0\u3051\u308c\u3070<ruby>\u6e08<rt>\u3059<\/rt><\/ruby>\u3080<strong>\u3082\u306e\u306e<\/strong>\u3001\u305d\u3053\u307e\u3067\u81ea\u5206\u3092\u304a\u3068\u3057\u3081\u308b\u3053\u3068\u304c\u3067\u304d\u306a\u304b\u3063\u305f\u3002<br>Although it would have ended better if he would have lost, he could not lower himself to such a degree.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>11. \u3042\u3093\u307e\u308a<ruby>\u5b09<rt>\u3046\u308c<\/rt><\/ruby>\u3057\u304b\u3063\u305f<strong>\u3082\u3093\u3067<\/strong>\u3001\u4f55\u3092\u3057\u3066\u308b\u306e\u304b\u306f\u5fd8\u308c\u3061\u307e\u3063\u305f\u3002(Really casual)<br>I was so happy that I forgot what I was doing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>12. \u4e00\u8a00\u3060\u3051\u8a71\u305b\u3070\u3088\u304b\u3063\u305f<strong>\u3082\u306e\u3092<\/strong>\u3001\u3057\u3083\u3079\u308a\u3059\u304e\u305f\u306e\u3067\u3001\u4e8b\u4ef6\u306b<ruby>\u5dfb<rt>\u307e<\/rt><\/ruby>\u304d\u8fbc\u307e\u308c\u3066\u3057\u307e\u3063\u305f\u3002<br>Although it would have been alright to speak just a word, I accidentally got involved into the matter\u00a0because I chattered too much.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>13. \u805e\u3044\u3066\u304f\u308c\u308c\u3070\u3088\u304b\u3063\u305f<strong>\u3082\u306e\u3092<\/strong>\u3002<br>If only he would have listened.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>14. \u3055\u3063\u3055\u3068\u8b66\u5bdf\u306b\u5c4a\u3051\u308a\u3083\u3044\u3044<strong>\u3082\u306e\u3092<\/strong>\u3002<br>If only I had given it to the police promptly.<br>From \u300e\u51b7\u305f\u3044\u8a98\u60d1\u300f by \u4e43\u5357\u30a2\u30b5.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Contraction Note<\/strong>: \u308a\u3083 is the contraction of \u308c\u3070.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>15. \u3082\u3063\u3068\u3046\u307e\u304f\u3067\u304d\u306a\u3044<strong>\u3082\u306e\u304b<\/strong>\uff1f<br>Can&#8217;t you do better?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>16. \u3053\u306e\u4ed5\u4e8b\u306f\u8ab0\u306b<ruby>\u983c<rt>\u305f\u306e<\/rt><\/ruby>\u3093\u3060<strong>\u3082\u306e\u304b<\/strong>\u3002<br>To whom was this work entrusted?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>17. \u6c17\u3065\u3044\u305f\u304b\u3089\u3044\u3044\u3088\u3046\u306a<strong>\u3082\u306e\u306e<\/strong>\u3001\u4ed6\u306e\u4eba\u304c\u3044\u305f\u3089\u3069\u3046\u3057\u305f\u3060\u308d\u3046\u304b\u3002<br>Though it is all right that I noticed, what would I do if there were other people?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>18. \u501f\u91d1\u3067\u56f0\u3063\u3066\u3044\u305f\u53cb\u4eba\u3092\u3001\u52a9\u3051\u3088\u3046\u3068\u601d\u3048\u3070\u52a9\u3051\u3089\u308c\u305f<strong>\u3082\u306e\u3092<\/strong>\u3001\u898b\u6368\u3066\u3066\u3057\u307e\u3063\u305f\u3002<br>If only I had thought to help my friend who was struggling with debt, I could have helped her, but I accidentally ran out on her.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>19. \u4f11\u3081\u3070\u3088\u304b\u3063\u305f<strong>\u3082\u306e\u3092<\/strong>\u3001\u7121\u7406\u3092\u3057\u3066\u50cd\u304d\u3059\u304e\u305f\u306e\u3067\u3001\u75c5\u6c17\u306b\u306a\u3063\u3066\u3057\u307e\u3063\u305f\u3088\u3002<br>Although I would have been fine if I took a rest, I unreasonably worked too much, so I ended up getting ill.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>20. \u3042\u305f\u3057\u306e\u6c17\u6301\u3061\u3001\u541b\u306b\u308f\u304b\u3063\u3066\u305f\u307e\u308b<strong>\u3082\u306e\u304b<\/strong>\uff01<br>How could you ever know how I&#8217;m feeling!?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Combination Particles with \u3082\u306e This lesson is about the particle \u3082\u306e and the\u00a0combination particles\u00a0associated wi<a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/imabi.org\/combination-particles-with-%e3%82%82%e3%81%ae\/\">\u7d9a\u304d\u3092\u8aad\u3080 <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">&#8220;Combination Particles with \u3082\u306e&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":158153075,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"advanced_seo_description":"","jetpack_seo_html_title":"","jetpack_seo_noindex":false,"jetpack_post_was_ever_published":false,"footnotes":""},"tags":[],"class_list":["post-749","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"jetpack_likes_enabled":true,"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/PeXUlI-c5","jetpack-related-posts":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/749","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/158153075"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=749"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/749\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12953,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/749\/revisions\/12953"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=749"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=749"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}